title: Friends (ASM aRticle)
description:
On episode 409 of Sleep and Relax ASMR, I read the wiki page for the classic and beloved sitcom Friends. This is another edition of ASM aRticles. 

Join along as I read about the premise and some adventures of Rachel, Ross, Joey, Phoebe, Monica, and Chandler. Enjoy!
